OL,3,C'Resilient' households behind slight
OL,4,Crise in consumer confidence
OL,6,FConsumer confidence rose slightly in
OL,7,FJanuary, driven by household
OL,8,F"resilience" rather than optimism
OL,9,Fabout the economy, figures show.
OL,11,FGfK's long-running Consumer Confidence
OL,12,FIndex increased by one point to minus
OL,13,F16, marking 10 years since the
OL,14,Fbarometer was last in positive
OL,15,Fterritory.
OL,17,FConfidence in personal finances over
OL,18,Fthe next year rose four points to six,
OL,19,Fwhich is eight points higher than this
OL,20,Ftime last year.
