OL,6,FHowever, expectations for the general
OL,7,Feconomic situation over the coming 12
OL,8,Fmonths fell two points to minus 31,
OL,9,Falthough this is three points higher
OL,10,Fthan last January.
OL,12,FThe Major Purchase Index ` a measure
OL,13,Fof confidence in buying big-ticket
OL,14,Fitems ` rose one point to minus 10, 10
OL,15,Fpoints higher than last year.
OL,17,FGfK consumer insights director Neil
OL,18,FBellamy said: "January 2026 brings an
OL,19,Funwanted anniversary, marking 10 years
OL,20,Fsince consumer confidence was last in
OL,21,Fpositive territory.
