OL,3,C'Resilient' households behind slight
OL,4,Crise in consumer confidence
OL,6,F"Even with a one-point increase in
OL,7,Fheadline confidence this month to
OL,8,Fminus 16, we remain a long way from
OL,9,Fconsumers feeling that better days are
OL,10,Faround the corner.
OL,12,F"Yes, perceptions of personal finances
OL,13,Fhave improved, but this is offset by
OL,14,Fgrowing concerns about the economy.
OL,16,F"We've seen this pattern before.
OL,17,FDuring periods of political and
OL,18,Feconomic uncertainty ` most notably in
OL,19,Flate 2022 ` consumers became more
OL,20,Fcautious but also more self-reliant.
