OL,3,C'Resilient' households behind slight
OL,4,Crise in consumer confidence
OL,6,F"What we're witnessing now is a return
OL,7,Fto that mindset: people feel they can
OL,8,Fmanage their own finances, but they
OL,9,Fremain unconvinced about the wider
OL,10,Feconomic outlook.
OL,12,F"Let's be clear, this isn't optimism;
OL,13,Fit's resilience.
OL,15,F"Consumers are once again focusing on
OL,16,Fwhat they can control ` their own
OL,17,Fspending and saving ` while confidence
OL,18,Fin the wider economy remains low.
